text: Middletown is the name of several places located in the U.S. state of New York: *Middletown, Delaware County, New York, a town *Middletown, Orange County, New York, a city *Middletown, Rockland County, New York, a former hamlet in the Town of Orangetown *Middletown, Richmond County, New York, a former incorporated town *Middletown (New Rochelle), a former hamlet in the Town of New Rochelle in Westchester County
title: Middletown, New York
